{"tid":2020424,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企隻貓係藍絲 應唔應該棄養？","createTime":"2020-05-17T05:05:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T07:41:29.000Z","uid":73381,"like":1387,"dislike":120,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"29f62ef1011f2e294c802a04f4f08aca9ce90456","tid":2020424,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T05:05:38.000Z","msg":"我養了貓貓五年 一直相安無事 直到去年開始 我才覺得有d唔妥<br />\n<br />\n電視每次描放tvb新聞 貓貓就會企係電視前好專住地睇 吸收哂d假新聞 放其他節目就佢做自己野<br />\n<br />\n從前佢最愛吃麥樂雞 但我地黃人拒食m記  我們轉了買mos麥樂雞給他吃 點知完全唔食 直到有次麥樂雞特價 我買了一點 貓貓吃到lanlan脷<br />\n<br />\n自此 我知道貓貓係藍絲<br />\n<br />\n想了很多方法想讓他轉黃 不停比佢睇rthk新聞 又餵佢食黃圈買的貓糧 但都好似冇咩用<br />\n<br />\n真的不想走到棄養一步。。。"},{"pid":"d9d48cc30ee4ec49ddff121ca0e5e39c5ef660d6","tid":2020424,"uid":293355,"like":36,"dislike":12,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T05:06:34.000Z","msg":"funny"},{"pid":"06baec019e05ccb1f87029540f07778f6eab9001","tid":2020424,"uid":154406,"like":140,"dislike":22,"score":118,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T05:06:38.000Z","msg":"人道毁滅啦"},{"pid":"2ebaae5ef3c5718d3990a4b15bb39d796079afeb","tid":2020424,"uid":34714,"like":23,"dislike":3,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T05:07:12.000Z","msg":"比我調教佢"},{"pid":"a60c2bbccf2775a8bed6b26e252b39fc95c72316","tid":2020424,"uid":138736,"like":119,"dislike":2,"score":117,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T05:07:22.000Z","msg":"似主人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"551d4a13d23adee5ce41cccb1cc5cf142b0f1a2d","tid":2020424,"uid":73381,"like":14,"dislike":32,"score":-18,"quote":{"pid":"a60c2bbccf2775a8bed6b26e252b39fc95c72316","tid":2020424,"uid":138736,"like":119,"dislike":2,"score":117,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T05:07:22.000Z","msg":"似主人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T05:09:13.000Z","msg":"我們一家都是黃人"},{"pid":"bd086ac7aa1cd0c702e19d435129c457fea6d3c6","tid":2020424,"uid":166677,"like":249,"dislike":10,"score":239,"citedBy":2,"replyTim